import React from 'react';
import {Container, Row, Col} from "react-bootstrap";

export const Home = (props) => (
    <>
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col sm={8}>sm=8</Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col sm>sm=true</Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    </>


)
